snippet.textDisplay: This is actually a traditional Rajasthan track which is still popular in weddings, the lyrics did undergo some changes like they're using "Raathoda" or "Saawaria" in the traditional one and "Raasila" in this new one. a great way to bring back the best of culture. Hats off to the very talented Mai for specially keeping that "Ghunghat" #Respect for that and I loved her voice, Atif needs no introduction, we all know he is amazing, they both nailed it together! Lots of respect and love!
